  "featureTourBack": "Back",
  "featureTourDesc0": "We will show you how the application works to help you track your nutrition, workouts, and daily habits in just 1 minute.",
  "featureTourDesc1": "Tap the (+) button to log food quickly:\n• Scan barcodes.\n• Use our private text or photo AI (fully anonymous).\n• Enter calories and macros manually.\n\nTap it right now to see it open!",
  "featureTourDesc10": "Access here to adjust your caloric requirements, change the language, metric/imperial units, or the application theme.\n\nTap the 'Profile' tab to continue.",
  "featureTourDesc11": "Link your account to sync your data in the cloud and schedule automatic encrypted backups to your Google Drive account.",
  "featureTourDesc12": "You have completed the interactive tour. Start logging your meals and habits today to reach your physical goal. Good luck!",
  "featureTourDesc2": "Your central panel calculates remaining calories in real time:\n• Adds base goals and subtracts food intake.\n• Monitors proteins, carbs, and fats to balance your day.",
  "featureTourDesc3": "Track your steps, sleep, and water. MacroTracker syncs automatically with Health Connect to import your data effortlessly.",
  "featureTourDesc4": "Track your evolution by logging body weight and measurements. View interactive trend charts to stay motivated.",
  "featureTourDesc5": "Receive smart weekly reports generated from your progress. The app will advise you how to adjust your plan to avoid plateaus.",
  "featureTourDesc6": "If your nutritionist uses the platform, you can link your account using their invite code to let them supervise and adapt your plan in real time.",
  "featureTourDesc7": "Organize your intakes by time of day (breakfast, lunch, snack, dinner) and perform continuous tracking of your habits.\n\nTap the 'Diary' tab on the bottom bar to continue.",
  "featureTourDesc8": "Review your daily intake. Tap any food to edit its grams or swipe to delete it if you made a mistake.",
  "featureTourDesc9": "Save your frequent meals in your library. Also, copy the link of any web recipe and our AI will import its ingredients automatically.",
